for infinite distance.

00:02:48.015 --> 00:02:51.630
It just, all over it would
have to decay exponentially.

00:02:51.630 --> 00:02:53.370
It's impossible.

00:02:53.370 --> 00:02:57.690
So all the energy
states, eigenstates here,

00:02:57.690 --> 00:03:00.260
